item.title: CVE-2017-16130|2024-09-17T03:43:42.412Z -- hackerone -- exxxxxxxxxxx%20node%20module
item.description: exxxxxxxxxxx is an Http eX Frame Google Style JavaScript Guide. exxxxxxxxxxx is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url. Accessible files are restricted to those with a file extension. Files with no extension such as /etc/passwd throw an error.
